ygData.messageBody:
Sorry I'm so late responding. I'm waaaaay behind on my email.
I was actually there bc I was called to ME to rez people. There were mob
corpses at zone after I was done. I asked if anyone wanted corpses at zone
and they said to go ahead and loot. So it was my lucky day. :-)
I won't venture far into zone without a group either.
luv,
-Su
